1
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:16,820
I've never understood one thing.

2
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:20,320
Why would someone like Cao Aiyuan,

3
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:22,600
who has a job, a family, and a seemingly stable life,

4
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:25,960
get involved with an ex-convict like Hua Weihong?

5
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:29,140
Have you ever been in love?

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:31,000
See,

7
00:00:31,080 --> 00:00:32,280
I can tell you haven't.

8
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:33,480
What do you know?

9
00:00:34,320 --> 00:00:35,600
Judging from your clothes,

10
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,400
your family must be quite well-off.

11
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:40,200
Why did you give up a stable job

12
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:43,000
to be a detective, facing danger all the time?

13
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:44,200
Right?

14
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:45,640
So,

15
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:48,600
sometimes choices don't need a reason.

16
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,240
Master.

17
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,160
Hurry.

18
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:11,120
You're a captain now.

19
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,650
Yet you still act like a kid.

20
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,640
Let me introduce you.

21
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:18,080
This is Comrade Zhang Ran from the Chudong CID.

22
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,920
And this is

23
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:22,560
Comrade Lin Wei from our Guangnan CID.

24
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,560
Hello, Comrade Lin.

25
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,080
Hello.

26
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:26,240
Captain Ma mentored me for a while after he transferred.

27
00:01:26,240 --> 00:01:27,000
Now that you're here,

28
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,600
just let me know if you need anything for the case.

29
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:31,120
We only have these five days.

30
00:01:31,120 --> 00:01:33,840
Is Chu Dong's Crown Nightclub far from here?

31
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,220
Not too far.

32
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:38,539
Then take us there right away. Hurry.

33
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,600
Our place is strictly legitimate.

34
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,039
Just singing and drinking.

35
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:45,000
Nothing else.

36
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,039
Did I ask you?

37
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,720
We're just here to look for someone.

38
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:49,440
Cooperate fully, and you'll be fine.

39
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,640
Okay, we've called everyone over.

40
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,840
They are in here. Ask whatever you want.

41
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,680
These officers have some questions for you.

42
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,410
Just answer whatever they ask.

43
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:03,880
Take a look.

44
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,800
Has anyone seen this girl?

45
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,360
This photo looks a bit familiar,

46
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,600
but I'm not entirely sure.

47
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,640
See if this looks like Azhi.

48
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,920
It does look a bit like her,

49
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,280
but the vibe is different.

50
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,640
Azhi has ion-permed hair.

51
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,040
She's very fashionable.

52
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:31,920
Who is Azhi?

53
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,480
Is Azhi here?

54
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,930
She asked for leave.

55
00:02:36,079 --> 00:02:37,610
Do you know where she lives?

56
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,280
No.

57
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,600
Are you guys close to Azhi?

58
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,730
Not really. She hasn't been here long.

59
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,880
When she comes to work, clients come to see her.

60
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,610
We don't get a chance to see her.

61
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,200
Then are you familiar with Azhi's clients?

62
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:53,800
Take me to see

63
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:56,000
the fire hydrants and fire extinguishers.

64
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,160
We have them all, Officer Zhang. These were just inspected last month.

65
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:01,840
Are you hiding something about your fire hydrants?

66
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,800
No, no, no.

67
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,400
If not, then take me there.

68
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,920
Okay, okay. Come this way.

69
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,280
Sorry to interrupt your work.

70
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,240
We are here,

71
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,040
and we don't want to take up too much of your time.

72
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:16,079
First, we're looking for the girl in the photo named Azhi.

73
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,440
We'll leave after asking.

74
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:19,900
You've all seen that girl named Azhi, right?

75
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,040
Do you know her well?

76
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:23,370
Not really. She just started not long ago.

77
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,720
Since she interacted with so many customers,

78
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,040
you guys must know them.

79
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:28,100
Who has the customers' information?

80
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,600
I do. I know.

81
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,720
Who are you?

82
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,050
Zheng Zhiqiang, right?

83
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,920
Police. We need to ask you a few questions.

84
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,860
Do you know her?

85
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,460
What's the matter?

86
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,680
It's nothing.

87
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:48,680
Let's talk outside.

88
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,940
Let's step out to talk.

89
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,040
Bro.

90
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,280
I do know Azhi.

91
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,120
But I only went to Crown Nightclub

92
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,440
to entertain clients.

93
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,880
The kind where I get invoices for reimbursement.

94
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,200
This girl named Azhi.

95
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,720
Did she ever ask you to go anywhere alone,

96
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,640
or did you meet her alone?

97
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,520
Officer,

98
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,800
you can't just say things like that.

99
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,440
My wife has all my money.

100
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:10,280
I don't have that kind of money.

101
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,080
All right.

102
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,440
If you see her again, remember to call the police.

103
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,280
Okay, okay.

104
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:37,920
You are...

105
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,050
Is this Hong Jinyi's house?

106
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,360
You are Hong Jinyi's...

107
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,400
I'm his wife.

108
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,280
Is he home?

109
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,640
He is not here. He went out for a business dinner.

110
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,440
With who?

111
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,600
I don't know.

112
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,240
Did something happen to him?

113
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,200
Nothing.

114
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,720
We are just doing a routine check.

115
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,650
Does he have a cell phone or a pager?

116
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,280
He has a cell phone.

117
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:08,400
(Hello, the number you have dialed is powered off.)

118
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,280
His phone is off.

119
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,540
Its battery might be dead.

120
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,280
Do you have any other way to contact him?

121
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,880
I'll try calling my cousin.

122
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,400
They're partners

123
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,040
and often go drinking together.

124
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,840
Please do it as soon as possible.

125
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,280
Sis.

126
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,200
Where is your brother-in-law?

127
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:32,600
My brother-in-law and Boss Tian are drunk.

128
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,400
They are hugging and crying,

129
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,200
reminiscing about the old days.

130
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:38,080
After crying, the deal will surely be done.

131
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,400
Is that what you mean?

132
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,930
I didn't spoil you for nothing.

133
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,220
Alright, let's go.

134
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:51,120
My cousin said he is drinking with Mr. Tian.

135
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,000
Mr. Tian is an old client of his.

136
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,520
Do you want him to come back right now?

137
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,520
No, it's fine.

138
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,640
Alright, sorry for bothering you.

139
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,770
I'll be leaving now.

140
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,400
I'll walk you out.

141
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,320
Mom.

142
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,580
Mom, Nuannuan.

143
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,200
Mom.

144
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,640
Who are they?

145
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,120
Nuannuan, they are...

146
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:17,480
I am a friend of your dad's.

147
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:19,360
I came to talk to him about something.

148
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:21,000
Did I disturb you?

149
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:24,240
This doll is so cute.

150
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,520
Her name is Little Nuannuan.

151
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:29,400
Then you must be Big Nuannuan.

152
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:31,200
Next time I come to see you,

153
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:33,120
I'll give you a beautiful butterfly sticker

154
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,480
to put on Nuannuan, okay?

155
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,240
Really?

156
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,320
Of course.

157
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,640
Thank you.

158
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,880
We'll be going now.

159
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,520
Okay.

160
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,840
Nuannuan,

161
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,200
it's getting late.

162
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,200
Time for bed.

163
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,280
Then you have to tell me a story.

164
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,480
Okay.

165
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,040
If your sister calls,

166
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,300
just say you're drunk.

167
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,520
Brother-in-law.

168
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,140
Almost forgot about this.

169
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,520
No, no.

170
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:09,440
This medicine is strong, take it easy.

171
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:11,370
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

172
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,170
It's better if it's strong.

173
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:14,960
Don't forget to pick me up tomorrow morning.

174
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:15,720
Alright, no problem.

175
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,120
Early.

176
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,720
Got it.

177
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,490
Take it easy.

178
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,290
Why look for Hong Jinyi?

179
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:42,520
I think Zheng Zhiqiang seems like an easier target.

180
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,840
He's just an employee.

181
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:47,120
He needs receipts to reimburse his spending at Crown.

182
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:49,240
There's not much money to make off him.

183
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,840
What about the guy Lao Er is watching?

184
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,520
He seems quite rich

185
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:53,560
and drives an imported car.

186
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,240
Boss Tian is indeed rich,

187
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,840
but his family is strict.

188
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:59,320
Going out is just for entertaining.

189
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,420
I tried a few times,

190
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,340
but he didn't take the bait at all.

191
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,640
Then it's Hong Jinyi.

192
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:09,920
Find a chance to lure him over recently,

193
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:11,970
and leave the rest to us.

194
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,360
Class is about to start, students.

195
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:20,800
Stand up.

196
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,240
Hello, students.

197
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,320
Hello, teacher.

198
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:30,840
Student Hong Xiaopang, keep drinking.

199
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,679
Damn, it's so late.

200
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,919
No, I have to go back first.

201
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,640
Waiter, bill please.

202
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,080
Stop right there.

203
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,020
Did I say class is over?

204
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:48,240
Student Hong Xiaopang is feeling a bit unwell.

205
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,640
I'd like to ask for sick leave

206
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,160
to go home early and rest.

207
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:55,240
I was going to take you to my private classroom

208
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,970
for some individual tutoring.

209
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:57,960
What a pity.

210
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,320
How about this?

211
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,280
If you finish class early some day,

212
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,240
If you are not busy,

213
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:07,720
let student Hong Xiaopang go to your private classroom alone

214
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:08,940
for some tutoring.

215
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:24,280
What is this place? It's so rundown.

216
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,840
Mr. Azhi,

217
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:54,720
Hong Xiaopang has arrived.

218
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:57,000
Come in, Xiaopang.

219
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,640
Okay.

220
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,640
Remember to close the door.

221
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,080
Understood.

222
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,520
Mr. Azhi.

223
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:17,320
Hong Xiaopang is reporting on time.

224
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,520
Good job, Xiaopang.

225
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:20,760
Since Xiaopang is doing so well,

226
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:23,490
shouldn't the teacher give the student a reward?

227
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,840
How about letting me give you a kiss?

228
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,690
Xiaopang is not being a good boy today.

229
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,280
Did I tell you to sit down?

230
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,120
Be good, Xiaopang.

231
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:43,120
Let Xiaopang give you a massage, okay?

232
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,080
I am not tired.

233
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:47,520
The skills Xiaopang just learned are really good.

234
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,440
You won't know until you try.

235
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:51,240
Let go, Xiaopang.

236
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,560
Let go.

237
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,400
You made a mistake today.

238
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,860
I won't teach you anymore.

239
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:03,880
Hong Jinyi, let go!

240
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,120
Stop pretending with me.

241
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,650
I came to this crappy place.

242
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:09,120
You put on glasses,

243
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,360
and pretend to be a teacher.

244
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,220
Let me tell you.

245
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,320
Today I will pretend to be a teacher

246
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,980
and teach you something else.

247
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,720
Let's go up.

248
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,080
Wait a bit longer.
